data.description: Your Backyard OASIS awaits! 4 bedroom 3 bath home with a formal dining that can be used as an office, game room upstairs, NEW paint, Roof 2021, HVAC 2022 with a gorgeous covered back patio looking out onto your pool with a hot tub and outdoor bar! Wylie ISD and NO HOA! Surrounded by new construction, three miles to Firewheel Mall, 7 minutes to Firewheel Golf Park (The Bridges), and about the same distance to George Bush Highway. The list of upgrades and improvements goes on! Attached to MLS Docs. Don't miss this gem in the middle of everything! Come see!
